gobblin.writer

Class SchemaBasedPartitionedDataWriterBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.writer.DataWriterBuilder<S,D>
      • gobblin.writer.PartitionAwareDataWriterBuilder<S,D>
        • gobblin.writer.FsDataWriterBuilder<Schema,GenericRecord>
          • gobblin.writer.AvroDataWriterBuilder
            • gobblin.writer.SchemaBasedPartitionedDataWriterBuilder

  • public class SchemaBasedPartitionedDataWriterBuilder
extends AvroDataWriterBuilder
    A DataWriterBuilder that uses name field of DataWriterBuilder.schema in path name and overrides getSchema() to use PartitionAwareDataWriterBuilder.partition Must be used with SchemaBasedWriterPartitioner
